<HL> ICC Sets March 2
For Its Next Move
In Rail-Merger Case</HL>
<DD> 02/04/87</DD>
<SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO>
<IN> SFX
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
